Interface NegatingFilter<F extends BaseFilter>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NotAcceptFilter, SQLNotFilter

    public interface NegatingFilter<F extends BaseFilter>
    An interface for BaseFilters that wrap another filter to negate its sense. This interface allows the original filter to be recovered if an additional negation is applied
